255
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:01,727
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm sorry.</b></i></font>

256
00:10:02,770 --> 00:10:04,897
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I understand
how you feel,</b></i></font>

257
00:10:04,981 --> 00:10:07,191
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but there's just nothing
more that I can do.</b></i></font>

258
00:10:07,275 --> 00:10:08,859
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How do you know
what I feel?</b></i></font>

259
00:10:08,943 --> 00:10:11,988
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't know what
