<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Whatever it is,
it's not as important
as this.</b></i></font>

480
00:19:14,738 --> 00:19:15,739
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What is this?</b></i></font>

481
00:19:15,823 --> 00:19:18,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's notice to suspend
William Sutter's
trading license.</b></i></font>

482
00:19:18,909 --> 00:19:21,245
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The question is,
what can be done about it?</b></i></font>

483
00:19:22,579 --> 00:19:23,622
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nothing can be done
about it.</b></i></font>

484
00:19:23,789 --> 00:19:24,998
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean,
"Nothing can be done
about it"?</b></i></font>

485
00:19:25,082 --> 00:19:26,333
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're supposed to be
the financial wizard.</b></i></font>

486
00:19:26,416 --> 00:19:27,543
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I am.</b></i></font>

487
00:19:27,626 --> 00:19:30,921
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm telling you
that this kind of thing's
up to the SEC's discretion.</b></i></font>

488
00:19:31,004 --> 00:19:33,507
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They have unlimited power
to suspend trading licenses
up to 90 days.</b></i></font>

489
00:19:33,590 --> 00:19:35,133
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>God damn it.
It's only 90 days.</b></i></font>

490
00:19:35,217 --> 00:19:36,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Ninety days gets me fired.</b></i></font>

491
00:19:36,593 --> 00:19:37,594
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, it's gonna
be okay, Harvey.</b></i></font>

492
00:19:37,678 --> 00:19:39,805
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know things have
been rough around here,
but business is...</b></i></font>

493
00:19:39,888 --> 00:19:42,140
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This isn't about
business, Louis.
It's about Mike.</b></i></font>

494
00:19:45,644 --> 00:19:46,979
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you not
telling me, Harvey?</b></i></font>

495
00:19:47,062 --> 00:19:48,146
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not going to
tell you the details,</b></i></font>

496
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:49,857
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because I'm not going
to put you at risk.</b></i></font>

497
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:51,567
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I have a chance
to get Mike out early</b></i></font>

498
00:19:51,650 --> 00:19:53,443
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and if I lose this motion,
it's over.</b></i></font>

499
00:19:54,695 --> 00:19:56,446
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, then, I'll figure out
a way to get it done.</b></i></font>

500
00:19:56,530 --> 00:19:57,531
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you, Louis.</b></i></font>

501
00:20:05,622 --> 00:20:06,748
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(CELL PHONE VIBRATING)</b></i></font>

502
00:20:06,999 --> 00:20:08,041
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is Harvey Specter.</b></i></font>

503
00:20:08,125 --> 00:20:09,543
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, it's me.
Mike.</b></i></font>

504
00:20:09,626 --> 00:20:11,253
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell are you doing
with a private phone?</b></i></font>

505
00:20:11,336 --> 00:20:12,880
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell are you doing
representing Kevin?</b></i></font>

506
00:20:12,963 --> 00:20:14,923
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You were the one
having trouble
getting him to open up.</b></i></font>

507
00:20:15,007 --> 00:20:17,885
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you thought telling him
not to trust anyone in here
was the answer to that?</b></i></font>

508
00:20:18,677 --> 00:20:20,888
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Look, I did that
to get him to trust me.</b></i></font>

509
00:20:20,971 --> 00:20:23,140
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because if he trusts me,
he trusts you.</b></i></font>

510
00:20:23,223 --> 00:20:25,267
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, well, you didn't
count on one thing.</b></i></font>

511
00:20:25,976 --> 00:20:28,270
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He knows I wasn't in the
infirmary the whole night.</b></i></font>

512
00:20:28,353 --> 00:20:30,397
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What? How the hell
does he know that?</b></i></font>

513
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:32,065
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Some guy he knows
works there.</b></i></font>

514
00:20:32,149 --> 00:20:35,068
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I told him some story about
you taking me to the hospital,
but he's not buying it.</b></i></font>

515
00:20:35,152 --> 00:20:37,321
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then you figure out a way
to make him buy it.</b></i></font>

516
00:20:37,487 --> 00:20:39,406
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Fine, I'll think
of something, but...</b></i></font>

517
00:20:40,324 --> 00:20:41,658
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not my only problem.</b></i></font>

518
00:20:41,825 --> 00:20:42,826
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What now?</b></i></font>

519
00:20:43,368 --> 00:20:44,912
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Gallo's filing came back.</b></i></font>

520
00:20:44,995 --> 00:20:46,371
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It needs to be filed
in person</b></i></font>

521
00:20:46,455 --> 00:20:48,373
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and it needs to be filed
by his attorney of record.</b></i></font>

522
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:50,417
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You got to be shitting me.</b></i></font>

523
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:52,419
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You want me to represent
that animal?</b></i></font>

524
00:20:52,669 --> 00:20:54,004
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you don't,
then getting Kevin to talk</b></i></font>

525
00:20:54,087 --> 00:20:55,464
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>is gonna be the least
of my problems.</b></i></font>

526
00:21:02,846 --> 00:21:04,598
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, I need your
help with something.</b></i></font>

527
00:21:05,390 --> 00:21:06,433
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What can I do?</b></i></font>

528
00:21:06,516 --> 00:21:09,227
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need you to draft a parole
application for Frank Gallo.</b></i></font>

529
00:21:09,311 --> 00:21:10,479
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I thought Mike
was doing that.</b></i></font>

530
00:21:10,562 --> 00:21:11,772
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There was a problem.</b></i></font>

531
00:21:11,855 --> 00:21:14,107
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which is also why
I need you to draw up
an engagement letter</b></i></font>

532
00:21:14,191 --> 00:21:15,651
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>for me to be
Gallo's attorney.</b></i></font>

533
00:21:17,694 --> 00:21:18,820
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Done.</b></i></font>

534
00:21:22,824 --> 00:21:24,409
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hey. What is it?</b></i></font>

535
00:21:25,869 --> 00:21:27,537
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I heard you get upset
with Louis earlier</b></i></font>

536
00:21:27,621 --> 00:21:29,873
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and now you're coming
to me about Gallo so...</b></i></font>

537
00:21:31,208 --> 00:21:32,292
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just need to know
if you think</b></i></font>

538
00:21:32,376 --> 00:21:34,086
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>this whole Cahill thing
is really going to work.</b></i></font>

539
00:21:34,503 --> 00:21:36,588
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel...
Harvey, just tell
me the truth.</b></i></font>

540
00:21:37,047 --> 00:21:38,799
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Look, I don't know if
it's gonna work or not.</b></i></font>

541
00:21:39,758 --> 00:21:41,969
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I do know I'm not
going to stop trying.</b></i></font>

542
00:21:48,058 --> 00:21:49,393
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Got to say,
you don't look so bad</b></i></font>

543
00:21:49,476 --> 00:21:51,728
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>for a guy who blacked out
in the yard the other day.</b></i></font>

544
00:21:52,229 --> 00:21:54,231
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, they...
They took good care of me.</b></i></font>

545
00:21:54,314 --> 00:21:55,482
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, I'm glad
you're okay.</b></i></font>

546
00:21:55,565 --> 00:21:56,733
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's on your mind?</b></i></font>

547
00:21:57,776 --> 00:21:59,695
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need you to get a message
to the warden for me.</b></i></font>

548
00:21:59,903 --> 00:22:02,906
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sure, I'll bring it to him
at our weekly brunch.</b></i></font>

549
00:22:03,490 --> 00:22:04,574
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What would you like
for it to say?</b></i></font>

550
00:22:04,658 --> 00:22:06,618
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm serious.
I don't care what you are.</b></i></font>

551
00:22:06,702 --> 00:22:07,786
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You want to get
a message to the warden,</b></i></font>

552
00:22:07,869 --> 00:22:08,870
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you go through
the proper channels</b></i></font>

553
00:22:08,954 --> 00:22:09,997
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and give it
to him yourself.</b></i></font>

554
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:11,123
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't go through
the proper channels</b></i></font>

555
00:22:11,206 --> 00:22:12,582
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because nobody
can know about it.</b></i></font>

556
00:22:14,584 --> 00:22:16,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>All right, Mike,
tell me what's going on.</b></i></font>

557
00:22:19,923 --> 00:22:21,466
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I made a deal
to get out of here early.</b></i></font>

558
00:22:21,758 --> 00:22:22,843
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What kind of deal?</b></i></font>

559
00:22:23,010 --> 00:22:24,761
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The kind where
I inform on someone.</b></i></font>

560
00:22:24,845 --> 00:22:25,846
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Someone?</b></i></font>

561
00:22:28,265 --> 00:22:29,850
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Kevin Miller.
Oh, Mike, come on.</b></i></font>

562
00:22:29,933 --> 00:22:32,185
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Julius, let me explain.
I don't need you to explain.</b></i></font>

563
00:22:32,269 --> 00:22:34,855
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're betraying
your cellmate who you
came to me to protect.</b></i></font>

564
00:22:34,938 --> 00:22:36,481
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No. What I am doing
is putting away</b></i></font>

565
00:22:36,565 --> 00:22:38,900
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>someone who is out there
doing worse things
than I ever did.</b></i></font>

566
00:22:38,984 --> 00:22:40,902
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So I don't need your
judgment, I need your help.</b></i></font>

567
00:22:40,986 --> 00:22:43,905
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm sorry. It's not
my job to help you
do something like this.</b></i></font>

568
00:22:43,989 --> 00:22:45,741
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, it's your job to help me
prepare for life after prison.</b></i></font>

569
00:22:45,824 --> 00:22:48,827
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, this is gonna
make life after prison
come a hell of a lot faster.</b></i></font>

570
00:22:48,952 --> 00:22:51,038
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, fine,
you wanna do this?
You go ahead and do it.</b></i></font>

571
00:22:51,121 --> 00:22:52,873
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm not going
to be complicit.</b></i></font>

572
00:22:52,956 --> 00:22:54,708
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You talk a big goddamn
game about trusting you,</b></i></font>

573
00:22:54,791 --> 00:22:56,043
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but what does
that trust mean?</b></i></font>

574
00:22:56,126 --> 00:22:57,711
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, I need to get
to the warden</b></i></font>

575
00:22:57,794 --> 00:22:59,546
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I need to do it without
the guards finding out.</b></i></font>

576
00:22:59,629 --> 00:23:00,964
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Can you help me or not?</b></i></font>

577
00:23:13,852 --> 00:23:16,146
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, what are
you doing here so late?</b></i></font>

578
00:23:16,271 --> 00:23:17,397
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Professor, do you
have a minute?</b></i></font>

579
00:23:17,481 --> 00:23:18,565
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course.</b></i></font>

580
00:23:18,648 --> 00:23:19,941
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah. Sit down.</b></i></font>

581
00:23:24,321 --> 00:23:25,489
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(SIGHS)</b></i></font>

582
00:23:26,406 --> 00:23:27,824
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I went to see
Leonard Bailey
this morning</b></i></font>

583
00:23:27,908 --> 00:23:29,743
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to tell him we were
turning our backs on him.</b></i></font>

584
00:23:29,826 --> 00:23:31,328
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No one's turning their
back on him, Rachel.</b></i></font>

585
00:23:31,411 --> 00:23:32,496
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There are just better cases.</b></i></font>

586
00:23:33,038 --> 00:23:34,706
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No offense,
but that's bullshit.</b></i></font>

587
00:23:35,373 --> 00:23:37,667
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Excuse me?
You read his file.</b></i></font>

588
00:23:37,793 --> 00:23:39,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's enough evidence
in there for him to get
a new trial</b></i></font>

589
00:23:40,003 --> 00:23:42,047
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and instead, we're going to
let him rot on death row.</b></i></font>

590
00:23:42,130 --> 00:23:43,340
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, I understand
how you feel but...</b></i></font>

591
00:23:43,423 --> 00:23:46,426
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I feel like I dropped your
class to take this case.</b></i></font>

592
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:48,512
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I told you
I'd get you another one.</b></i></font>

593
00:23:48,595 --> 00:23:49,930
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want another one.</b></i></font>

594
00:23:50,013 --> 00:23:51,098
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want this one.</b></i></font>

595
00:23:51,181 --> 00:23:54,768
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, I cannot provide
you with the resources
and the backing anymore.</b></i></font>

596
00:23:54,851 --> 00:23:56,937
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay. So, what if I were able
to provide my own resources</b></i></font>

597
00:23:57,020 --> 00:23:59,981
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and to get the supervision
of a qualified lawyer?</b></i></font>

598
00:24:01,024 --> 00:24:02,359
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you talking about?</b></i></font>

599
00:24:02,692 --> 00:24:04,986
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I work at Pearson
Specter Litt, Professor.</b></i></font>

600
00:24:05,570 --> 00:24:08,448
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They've been known to
take a pro bono case
from time to time.</b></i></font>

601
00:24:12,119 --> 00:24:14,746
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay.
Okay, you win, Rachel.</b></i></font>

602
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:16,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But this is highly irregular.</b></i></font>

603
00:24:16,873 --> 00:24:18,083
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't care.</b></i></font>

604
00:24:18,166 --> 00:24:19,251
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not
a good enough reason</b></i></font>

605
00:24:19,334 --> 00:24:20,794
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to turn our backs
on Leonard Bailey.</b></i></font>

606
00:24:24,798 --> 00:24:27,008
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, don't ever question
my financial wizardry again.</b></i></font>

607
00:24:27,092 --> 00:24:28,135
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Let's have it.</b></i></font>

608
00:24:28,218 --> 00:24:29,261
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I was banging my head
against the wall</b></i></font>

609
00:24:29,344 --> 00:24:31,054
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>trying to figure out a way
to stop the suspension.</b></i></font>

610
00:24:31,138 --> 00:24:32,848
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But then it dawned on me.
We don't need to stop it.</b></i></font>

611
00:24:32,931 --> 00:24:36,101
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If we can turn Sutter's firm
into the subsidiary of
a separate holding company,</b></i></font>

612
00:24:36,226 --> 00:24:39,062
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>we can find someone else
to execute the trades for him.
Beautiful.</b></i></font>

613
00:24:39,146 --> 00:24:40,689
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, but the only issue
is we need to find traders</b></i></font>

614
00:24:40,772 --> 00:24:42,357
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that are willing to bankroll
the son of a bitch,</b></i></font>

615
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,608
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>given his reputation.</b></i></font>

616
00:24:43,692 --> 00:24:44,693
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, that's not going
to be a problem.</b></i></font>

617
00:24:44,776 --> 00:24:45,944
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, Harvey,
this is not nothing.</b></i></font>

618
00:24:46,027 --> 00:24:47,946
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nobody wants to work
with this guy.</b></i></font>

619
00:24:48,029 --> 00:24:49,489
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're forgetting our
new friends across the hall.</b></i></font>

620
00:24:49,948 --> 00:24:51,116
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What, are you kidding me?</b></i></font>

621
00:24:51,199 --> 00:24:52,993
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You think that asshole
is going to say yes to me?</b></i></font>

622
00:24:53,076 --> 00:24:55,537
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's okay. I know
who he'll say yes to.</b></i></font>

623
00:24:57,497 --> 00:24:58,623
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hey, Harvey.</b></i></font>

624
00:24:59,040 --> 00:25:01,835
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know how tough it's been,
not having Mike here,
and I...</b></i></font>

625
00:25:01,918 --> 00:25:04,254
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just want to let you know
I miss him, too.</b></i></font>

626
00:25:04,337 --> 00:25:06,506
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I appreciate that, Louis,
but you didn't have
to say it,</b></i></font>

627
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:08,008
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because actions
speak louder than words.</b></i></font>

628
00:25:08,091 --> 00:25:10,260
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you doing this
says it all.</b></i></font>

629
00:25:18,393 --> 00:25:20,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I've been
looking for you all day.</b></i></font>

630
00:25:20,103 --> 00:25:21,188
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, here I am.</b></i></font>

631
00:25:21,354 --> 00:25:23,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then maybe you can tell me
why all of a sudden,</b></i></font>

632
00:25:23,523 --> 00:25:24,941
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>we're representing
William Sutter?</b></i></font>

633
00:25:25,025 --> 00:25:27,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I changed my mind.
You changed your mind.</b></i></font>

634
00:25:27,402 --> 00:25:31,239
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You told me taking
Sutter on would be
like selling your soul.</b></i></font>

635
00:25:31,323 --> 00:25:32,824
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And now, you're doing
a complete 180.</b></i></font>

636
00:25:32,908 --> 00:25:34,576
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Jessica, I...
No.</b></i></font>

637
00:25:34,659 --> 00:25:36,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, I'm not saying
I don't like it.</b></i></font>

638
00:25:36,703 --> 00:25:37,954
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just want to know
what's going on.</b></i></font>

639
00:25:38,622 --> 00:25:40,624
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sutter's the one
Cahill's after.</b></i></font>

640
00:25:41,124 --> 00:25:42,292
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, you've got
to be kidding me.</b></i></font>

641
00:25:42,375 --> 00:25:43,418
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I shit you not.</b></i></font>

642
00:25:44,169 --> 00:25:46,171
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Ah. Well, I get it.</b></i></font>

643
00:25:47,297 --> 00:25:49,257
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You give him
a full-throttle defense,</b></i></font>

644
00:25:49,341 --> 00:25:50,800
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>gain his trust,</b></i></font>

645
00:25:50,884 --> 00:25:52,719
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and hope to God
Mike cuts his legs out.</b></i></font>

646
00:25:52,802 --> 00:25:53,803
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Exactly.</b></i></font>

647
00:25:55,305 --> 00:25:56,306
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

648
00:25:56,389 --> 00:25:58,433
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Is he going to give us
his investment business?</b></i></font>

649
00:25:58,516 --> 00:25:59,893
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Not until after we win.</b></i></font>

650
00:25:59,976 --> 00:26:01,561
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which we're
hoping we don't.</b></i></font>

651
00:26:01,645 --> 00:26:04,898
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Jessica, I have to do this.
Harvey, relax. I'm onboard.</b></i></font>

652
00:26:04,981 --> 00:26:07,943
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It pays the bills
and we can leverage it
into more business anyway.</b></i></font>

653
00:26:08,026 --> 00:26:10,278
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But we better
leverage it fast,</b></i></font>

654
00:26:10,362 --> 00:26:12,030
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because losing this case
might be good for Mike,</b></i></font>

655
00:26:12,113 --> 00:26:13,657
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but it's not going
to be good for us.</b></i></font>

656
00:26:14,157 --> 00:26:15,575
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I don't know about you,</b></i></font>

657
00:26:15,659 --> 00:26:17,035
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but I'd like
to get back on top.</b></i></font>

658
00:26:17,118 --> 00:26:18,662
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's nothing
I'd like more.</b></i></font>

659
00:26:18,787 --> 00:26:20,163
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which is why I came in here.</b></i></font>

660
00:26:20,914 --> 00:26:21,915
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you need?</b></i></font>

661
00:26:21,998 --> 00:26:24,125
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need you to get something
from those traders.</b></i></font>

662
00:26:27,045 --> 00:26:28,672
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(DOOR BUZZING)</b></i></font>

663
00:26:29,589 --> 00:26:30,924
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>On your feet, Ross.</b></i></font>

664
00:26:31,007 --> 00:26:32,509
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're going to solitary.
What?</b></i></font>

665
00:26:32,592 --> 00:26:33,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Wait, what are
you talking about?</b></i></font>

666
00:26:33,843 --> 00:26:35,595
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You heard me.
24 hours. Let's go.</b></i></font>

667
00:26:35,679 --> 00:26:36,805
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, I'm not going
anywhere with you</b></i></font>

668
00:26:36,888 --> 00:26:37,889
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>until you tell me
what's going on.</b></i></font>

669
00:26:37,973 --> 00:26:40,183
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You'll go where I tell
you to, or you'll get
acquainted with this.</b></i></font>

670
00:26:40,267 --> 00:26:42,102
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Listen to me.
I just want to know why...</b></i></font>

671
00:26:42,185 --> 00:26:44,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Next question
makes it 48 hours.</b></i></font>

672
00:26:45,689 --> 00:26:46,856
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You coming or not?</b></i></font>

673
00:26:49,317 --> 00:26:50,485
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What did you do?</b></i></font>

674
00:26:58,702 --> 00:27:00,036
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Jessica, good,
I caught you.</b></i></font>

675
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,705
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, what is it?</b></i></font>

676
00:27:01,788 --> 00:27:03,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Do you remember
my Innocence Project case?</b></i></font>

677
00:27:03,873 --> 00:27:05,709
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How could I not?
Badass Rachel.</b></i></font>

678
00:27:06,418 --> 00:27:07,627
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.
So, I took it,</b></i></font>

679
00:27:07,711 --> 00:27:09,462
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but now they're saying
that it doesn't qualify.</b></i></font>

680
00:27:10,213 --> 00:27:12,465
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Let me guess. You want us
to take it on as a pro bono.</b></i></font>

681
00:27:12,549 --> 00:27:14,551
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>All I need is one hour
a week of supervision</b></i></font>

682
00:27:14,634 --> 00:27:17,387
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and if I need to appear
in court, you come with me.</b></i></font>

683
00:27:17,470 --> 00:27:18,972
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know that's a lot
to ask, but...</b></i></font>

684
00:27:19,055 --> 00:27:20,640
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, I wish
I could tell you</b></i></font>

685
00:27:20,724 --> 00:27:22,434
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I had an extra hour
to give, but I don't.</b></i></font>

686
00:27:22,517 --> 00:27:23,810
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Jessica, please.</b></i></font>

687
00:27:24,227 --> 00:27:26,438
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you would just come
with me and meet this man.</b></i></font>

688
00:27:26,521 --> 00:27:27,605
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, this is my point.</b></i></font>

689
00:27:27,856 --> 00:27:30,400
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just found out we have
less time than I thought
we did</b></i></font>

690
00:27:30,483 --> 00:27:31,735
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to get this firm
back on its feet,</b></i></font>

691
00:27:31,818 --> 00:27:34,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I can't afford to spend
one minute on anything else.</b></i></font>

692
00:27:34,904 --> 00:27:36,656
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But, I mean, really...
Rachel,</b></i></font>

693
00:27:38,074 --> 00:27:39,159
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm sorry.</b></i></font>

694
00:27:40,368 --> 00:27:41,745
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, if you'll excuse me...</b></i></font>

695
00:27:57,093 --> 00:27:58,094
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.</b></i></font>

696
00:27:58,178 --> 00:27:59,846
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank your counselor,
Mr. Rowe.</b></i></font>

697
00:27:59,929 --> 00:28:01,931
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I will.
You must trust him a lot</b></i></font>

698
00:28:02,057 --> 00:28:04,100
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to let him in on your
little arrangement.</b></i></font>

699
00:28:04,184 --> 00:28:05,226
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I do.</b></i></font>

700
00:28:05,393 --> 00:28:07,979
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And he helped me even though
he doesn't approve of this.</b></i></font>

701
00:28:09,564 --> 00:28:10,607
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It sounds like
you don't either.</b></i></font>

702
00:28:10,732 --> 00:28:12,567
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's not up to me
to approve or not.</b></i></font>

703
00:28:12,650 --> 00:28:14,069
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Is that what you came
down here to tell me?</b></i></font>

704
00:28:14,152 --> 00:28:16,988
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, I came down here
to tell you I've been
doing this a long time.</b></i></font>

705
00:28:17,655 --> 00:28:19,866
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I've seen a lot
of inmates come and go.</b></i></font>

706
00:28:20,742 --> 00:28:23,078
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>These kind of deals,
they don't always
work out so well.</b></i></font>

707
00:28:23,787 --> 00:28:26,206
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You saying
you think I'll be here
for the whole two years?</b></i></font>

708
00:28:26,289 --> 00:28:29,084
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm saying I hope
it doesn't turn out
even worse than that.</b></i></font>

709
00:28:49,312 --> 00:28:50,814
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I thought the markets
were closed.</b></i></font>

710
00:28:51,815 --> 00:28:54,025
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Haven't you ever seen
Wall Street?
Money never sleeps.</b></i></font>

711
00:28:56,319 --> 00:28:57,320
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's this?</b></i></font>

712
00:28:57,695 --> 00:28:58,822
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Have a look.</b></i></font>

713
00:29:00,490 --> 00:29:01,449
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Let me get this straight.</b></i></font>

714
00:29:01,533 --> 00:29:03,743
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I hire you and
the first thing you do
is come to me for a favor?</b></i></font>

715
00:29:03,827 --> 00:29:06,454
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I came to you for a favor
when you were my tenant.</b></i></font>

716
00:29:06,579 --> 00:29:09,249
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, as your lawyer,
I'm coming to you
with an opportunity.</b></i></font>

717
00:29:09,332 --> 00:29:10,375
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you talking about?</b></i></font>

718
00:29:10,458 --> 00:29:12,001
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's not
a charitable donation.</b></i></font>

719
00:29:12,293 --> 00:29:14,421
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You do this,
you'll get paid for it.</b></i></font>

720
00:29:14,504 --> 00:29:15,839
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How much?
Enough.</b></i></font>

721
00:29:15,922 --> 00:29:17,507
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How do I know I'm not leaving
something on the table?</b></i></font>

722
00:29:17,590 --> 00:29:19,801
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I never leave
anything on the table.</b></i></font>

723
00:29:21,678 --> 00:29:22,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>All right.</b></i></font>

724
00:29:26,516 --> 00:29:27,725
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You know, I don't get it.</b></i></font>

725
00:29:29,227 --> 00:29:30,437
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're obviously
a big-time attorney,</b></i></font>

726
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:32,689
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and now you're
sub-letting to me.</b></i></font>

727
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,649
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell happened here?</b></i></font>

728
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:36,443
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't know?</b></i></font>

729
00:29:36,526 --> 00:29:37,527
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why would I?</b></i></font>

730
00:29:37,777 --> 00:29:38,862
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Google it.</b></i></font>

731
00:29:39,446 --> 00:29:40,530
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That bad.</b></i></font>

732
00:29:40,613 --> 00:29:43,241
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We hired a lawyer.
Turns out he was a fraud.</b></i></font>

733
00:29:43,324 --> 00:29:44,742
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It ruined our reputation.</b></i></font>

734
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:47,662
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Turned out to be a fraud
or you knew he was a fraud?</b></i></font>

735
00:29:48,455 --> 00:29:50,915
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Good night, Stu.
See you in the morning.</b></i></font>

736
00:30:00,884 --> 00:30:01,885
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(DOOR BUZZING)</b></i></font>

737
00:30:03,803 --> 00:30:05,305
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Warden, what are you doing?</b></i></font>

738
00:30:05,388 --> 00:30:06,473
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Did you know Mike Ross</b></i></font>

739
00:30:06,556 --> 00:30:07,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>left the prison grounds
the other night?</b></i></font>

740
00:30:07,891 --> 00:30:09,142
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?
Don't bullshit me.</b></i></font>

741
00:30:09,225 --> 00:30:10,810
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Did you know his lawyer,
who I understand</b></i></font>

742
00:30:10,894 --> 00:30:12,061
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>is now also your lawyer,</b></i></font>

743
00:30:12,145 --> 00:30:13,229
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>paid someone
to get him out of here?</b></i></font>

744
00:30:13,313 --> 00:30:14,939
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't know
anything about it.</b></i></font>

745
00:30:15,023 --> 00:30:17,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I suppose if I asked
you who he paid,
you'd have the same answer.</b></i></font>

746
00:30:18,735 --> 00:30:23,323
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I find out you're lying,
next time, you are going
to be the one in solitary.</b></i></font>

747
00:30:23,406 --> 00:30:24,782
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And it won't be
just one night.</b></i></font>

748
00:30:48,598 --> 00:30:49,641
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

749
00:30:49,933 --> 00:30:51,726
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm just thinking about
when this asshole finds out</b></i></font>

750
00:30:51,809 --> 00:30:54,187
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you're going to blow
his bullshit suspension
out of the water.</b></i></font>

751
00:30:54,646 --> 00:30:57,232
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>William, I am going to blow
it out of the water.</b></i></font>

752
00:30:57,315 --> 00:30:59,817
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm going to need you
to sign this first.</b></i></font>

753
00:31:02,445 --> 00:31:04,822
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell is
Stevens Investment Group?</b></i></font>

754
00:31:04,906 --> 00:31:06,824
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's the company you're
trading through from now on.</b></i></font>

755
00:31:06,908 --> 00:31:07,909
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit.</b></i></font>

756
00:31:07,992 --> 00:31:10,161
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They own me?
They don't own anything.</b></i></font>

757
00:31:10,245 --> 00:31:11,663
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They control you on paper.</b></i></font>

758
00:31:11,746 --> 00:31:14,290
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And unless you want to shut
down for the next 90 days,</b></i></font>

759
00:31:14,374 --> 00:31:16,376
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>this is what you have to do.
Well, it's bullshit.</b></i></font>

760
00:31:16,709 --> 00:31:18,545
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you going to do
if that guy indicts me,</b></i></font>

761
00:31:18,628 --> 00:31:20,755
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>cut a deal where I plead
guilty and I get probation?</b></i></font>

762
00:31:20,838 --> 00:31:22,632
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because if this is what
you consider winning,</b></i></font>

763
00:31:22,715 --> 00:31:24,050
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I might as well find
myself another lawyer.</b></i></font>

764
00:31:24,676 --> 00:31:27,428
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay, gentlemen.
I'm ready to hear arguments.</b></i></font>

765
00:31:27,845 --> 00:31:28,888
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I have to tell you,</b></i></font>

766
00:31:28,972 --> 00:31:31,140
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>unless Congress passed
a new law last night,</b></i></font>

767
00:31:31,307 --> 00:31:32,809
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>this suspension stands.</b></i></font>

768
00:31:37,105 --> 00:31:38,231
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's okay, Your Honor.</b></i></font>

769
00:31:38,314 --> 00:31:40,984
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>My client's firm
is now the subsidiary</b></i></font>

770
00:31:41,067 --> 00:31:43,987
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>of a holding company with
a different trading license.
What?</b></i></font>

771
00:31:44,153 --> 00:31:45,154
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's all right here.</b></i></font>

772
00:31:45,655 --> 00:31:48,408
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>In that case, I move
to have that company's
license suspended.</b></i></font>

773
00:31:48,491 --> 00:31:51,327
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And that, right there,
is why I'd like
to ask the court</b></i></font>

774
00:31:51,411 --> 00:31:53,621
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to have Mr. Cahill removed
from any investigation</b></i></font>

775
00:31:53,705 --> 00:31:55,123
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>regarding my client
in the future.</b></i></font>

776
00:31:55,206 --> 00:31:56,624
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are you out of your mind?</b></i></font>

777
00:31:57,166 --> 00:31:59,752
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We have an antagonistic
history, Your Honor.</b></i></font>

778
00:31:59,836 --> 00:32:00,920
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Everyone knows it,</b></i></font>

779
00:32:01,004 --> 00:32:03,423
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and this action
is nothing more than a stunt</b></i></font>

780
00:32:03,506 --> 00:32:05,216
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>designed to punish me
through my client.</b></i></font>

781
00:32:05,300 --> 00:32:06,301
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is ridiculous.</b></i></font>

782
00:32:06,384 --> 00:32:08,845
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've been investigating
William Sutter for 18 months.</b></i></font>

783
00:32:08,928 --> 00:32:11,598
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And in the last 18 months,
he took no action.</b></i></font>

784
00:32:11,681 --> 00:32:15,435
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And then yesterday,
when I informed him
I am Mr. Sutter's attorney,</b></i></font>

785
00:32:15,518 --> 00:32:17,770
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>within five hours,
he suspends his license.</b></i></font>

786
00:32:17,854 --> 00:32:19,397
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And now,
he's trying to do it again.</b></i></font>

787
00:32:20,690 --> 00:32:22,066
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's what I call a win.</b></i></font>

788
00:32:22,734 --> 00:32:24,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>JUDGE: Mr. Cahill,
this doesn't look good.</b></i></font>

789
00:32:24,527 --> 00:32:26,321
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm inclined to take
you off this case.</b></i></font>

790
00:32:26,404 --> 00:32:28,531
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Your Honor,
Mr. Specter is right.</b></i></font>

791
00:32:28,615 --> 00:32:29,782
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We have history.</b></i></font>

792
00:32:29,866 --> 00:32:32,118
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I've been involved in this
case a lot longer than he has.</b></i></font>

793
00:32:32,201 --> 00:32:34,203
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, if anyone needs to be
thrown off for a conflict,</b></i></font>

794
00:32:34,287 --> 00:32:35,622
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>it is him, not me.</b></i></font>

795
00:32:35,705 --> 00:32:37,290
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not going anywhere,
Your Honor.</b></i></font>

796
00:32:37,373 --> 00:32:39,959
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then let Mr. Sutter waive any
claims to conflict altogether.</b></i></font>

797
00:32:40,043 --> 00:32:41,419
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Unless, of course,
you want to set a precedent</b></i></font>

798
00:32:41,502 --> 00:32:43,796
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that anytime a defendant
doesn't like his prosecutor,</b></i></font>

799
00:32:43,880 --> 00:32:45,256
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>all he has to do
is hire a lawyer</b></i></font>

800
00:32:45,340 --> 00:32:46,466
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>he's gone up against before.</b></i></font>

801
00:32:47,592 --> 00:32:48,676
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>JUDGE: Mr. Sutter,</b></i></font>

802
00:32:49,636 --> 00:32:51,387
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>would you like to keep your
attorney or hire another one?</b></i></font>

803
00:32:51,471 --> 00:32:53,765
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I am not taking
Mr. Cahill off this case.</b></i></font>

804
00:32:59,562 --> 00:33:01,064
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey's my guy, Your Honor.</b></i></font>

805
00:33:02,607 --> 00:33:05,902
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then unless
there's some other issue,
the court has a full docket.</b></i></font>

806
00:33:21,542 --> 00:33:23,836
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Guard tells you
you have a visitor
and doesn't say who it is,</b></i></font>

807
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:27,423
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you start thinking maybe
Angelina Jolie opened
your letters after all.</b></i></font>

808
00:33:27,507 --> 00:33:28,675
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sit down, Gallo.</b></i></font>

809
00:33:28,758 --> 00:33:30,927
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You here to make
more false accusations?</b></i></font>

810
00:33:31,010 --> 00:33:34,055
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm here to tell you
that, as of this minute,
I'm your new attorney.</b></i></font>

811
00:33:34,514 --> 00:33:35,598
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Come again?</b></i></font>

812
00:33:35,682 --> 00:33:37,809
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You need someone
to file that motion.</b></i></font>

813
00:33:38,226 --> 00:33:40,687
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm that someone.
What if I don't
want your help?</b></i></font>

814
00:33:40,770 --> 00:33:41,771
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, then,
you can rot in here</b></i></font>

815
00:33:41,854 --> 00:33:43,106
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>for the rest
of your sentence.</b></i></font>

816
00:33:46,734 --> 00:33:48,361
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's actually kind of funny,
isn't it?</b></i></font>

817
00:33:49,195 --> 00:33:51,030
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You fighting to get me out</b></i></font>

818
00:33:51,114 --> 00:33:52,907
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>when you fought so hard
to put me away.</b></i></font>

819
00:33:53,491 --> 00:33:54,701
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Must kill you.</b></i></font>

820
00:33:54,784 --> 00:33:56,285
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Makes me sick
to my stomach.</b></i></font>

821
00:33:57,412 --> 00:33:58,454
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But...</b></i></font>

822
00:33:58,955 --> 00:34:01,833
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm going to live with it,
because you're going to
give me something in return.</b></i></font>

823
00:34:01,916 --> 00:34:03,459
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, yeah? What's that?</b></i></font>

824
00:34:03,710 --> 00:34:05,128
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Until this thing
goes through,</b></i></font>

825
00:34:05,211 --> 00:34:07,588
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>not only are you going
to keep your hands off Mike,</b></i></font>

826
00:34:07,672 --> 00:34:09,507
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you're going to be his
personal protector in here.</b></i></font>

827
00:34:09,590 --> 00:34:11,008
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bullshit.
Not bullshit.</b></i></font>

828
00:34:11,092 --> 00:34:14,887
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He so much as twists
an ankle in the yard,
I'll withdraw that motion.</b></i></font>

829
00:34:14,971 --> 00:34:17,140
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Aren't you forgetting
a little something, champ?</b></i></font>

830
00:34:17,640 --> 00:34:19,225
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't need you to handle
this thing for me.</b></i></font>

831
00:34:19,308 --> 00:34:22,228
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now that I know what's what,
I'll get my own attorney.</b></i></font>

832
00:34:22,311 --> 00:34:24,063
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah. You do that
and I'll tell the courts</b></i></font>

833
00:34:24,147 --> 00:34:27,358
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that you just admitted to me
that you tried to poison Mike.</b></i></font>

834
00:34:27,442 --> 00:34:29,235
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You know how much time
that's going to add
to your sentence?</b></i></font>

835
00:34:29,318 --> 00:34:30,987
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I didn't do shit to him!
Good for you.</b></i></font>

836
00:34:31,112 --> 00:34:32,405
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Who do you think
they're going to believe?</b></i></font>

837
00:34:32,488 --> 00:34:34,198
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>A former prosecutor like me</b></i></font>

838
00:34:34,282 --> 00:34:36,492
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>or an informant
convict like you?</b></i></font>

839
00:34:37,618 --> 00:34:39,829
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course,
if I'm your attorney,</b></i></font>

840
00:34:40,580 --> 00:34:42,248
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't tell them
any of that.</b></i></font>

841
00:34:42,331 --> 00:34:43,332
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(CHUCKLES)</b></i></font>

842
00:34:44,417 --> 00:34:45,793
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You son of a bitch.</b></i></font>

843
00:34:46,502 --> 00:34:47,628
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You set me up.</b></i></font>

844
00:34:47,712 --> 00:34:49,046
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I sure as hell did.</b></i></font>

845
00:34:49,964 --> 00:34:51,299
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, it's up to you.</b></i></font>

846
00:34:53,134 --> 00:34:55,178
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You in or you out?</b></i></font>

847
00:35:03,186 --> 00:35:04,353
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Can I talk to you a second?</b></i></font>

848
00:35:04,437 --> 00:35:05,563
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What is it, Louis?</b></i></font>

849
00:35:06,564 --> 00:35:07,774
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't find a house.</b></i></font>

850
00:35:08,024 --> 00:35:09,609
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>House? What house?</b></i></font>

851
00:35:10,401 --> 00:35:11,611
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't know anything
about a house.</b></i></font>

852
00:35:11,694 --> 00:35:13,029
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Certainly not for a person</b></i></font>

853
00:35:13,112 --> 00:35:14,781
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>who doesn't have any
confidence in my ability</b></i></font>

854
00:35:14,864 --> 00:35:16,657
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to know what he's looking
for in a given situation.</b></i></font>

855
00:35:16,741 --> 00:35:17,784
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna, please.
Can't we just pretend</b></i></font>

856
00:35:17,867 --> 00:35:19,535
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that I didn't say what I said
like we usually do?</b></i></font>

857
00:35:19,619 --> 00:35:20,620
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, Louis. We can't.</b></i></font>

858
00:35:20,745 --> 00:35:22,914
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I need to know
that you have spent
at least one second</b></i></font>

859
00:35:22,997 --> 00:35:25,041
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>contemplating what your
little outburst was about.</b></i></font>

860
00:35:31,714 --> 00:35:33,132
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know what it was about.</b></i></font>

861
00:35:34,008 --> 00:35:35,218
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Really? What is that?</b></i></font>

862
00:35:37,553 --> 00:35:38,888
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I miss you, Donna.</b></i></font>

863
00:35:40,723 --> 00:35:44,018
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I miss having you
as my secretary.</b></i></font>

864
00:35:48,397 --> 00:35:49,982
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I miss you, too, Louis.
And don't get me wrong.</b></i></font>

865
00:35:50,066 --> 00:35:51,734
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not saying
Gretchen's not great.</b></i></font>

866
00:35:51,818 --> 00:35:53,152
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Who would?
It's just...</b></i></font>

867
00:35:54,195 --> 00:35:56,072
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm just saying
she's not you.</b></i></font>

868
00:35:57,615 --> 00:35:59,075
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Who is?
Nobody.</b></i></font>

869
00:36:05,248 --> 00:36:06,666
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Is this the kind of thing
you're looking for?</b></i></font>

870
00:36:06,916 --> 00:36:09,460
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, my God, it's perfect.
Is it still available?</b></i></font>

871
00:36:09,585 --> 00:36:10,837
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>An offer
went in this morning.</b></i></font>

872
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:13,422
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We have to beat it.
No, Louis, we don't.</b></i></font>

873
00:36:14,173 --> 00:36:15,174
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That offer was yours.</b></i></font>

874
00:36:19,136 --> 00:36:20,346
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Did they take it?</b></i></font>

875
00:36:20,429 --> 00:36:21,472
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We find out tomorrow.</b></i></font>

876
00:36:23,975 --> 00:36:25,393
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna.</b></i></font>

877
00:36:25,476 --> 00:36:26,477
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No.</b></i></font>

878
00:36:30,189 --> 00:36:31,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(DOOR BUZZING)</b></i></font>

879
00:36:35,903 --> 00:36:37,405
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(SIGHS)</b></i></font>

880
00:36:41,617 --> 00:36:43,119
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Sorry about what happened
with the warden.</b></i></font>

881
00:36:43,369 --> 00:36:44,412
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah.</b></i></font>

882
00:36:46,789 --> 00:36:47,957
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you need anything...</b></i></font>

883
00:36:48,457 --> 00:36:49,667
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'll let you know.</b></i></font>

884
00:36:58,009 --> 00:37:00,219
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Look, I didn't tell him
what you told me</b></i></font>

885
00:37:00,303 --> 00:37:01,762
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>about Harvey
getting you out.</b></i></font>

886
00:37:02,346 --> 00:37:04,015
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need you to know that.
It's important to me.</b></i></font>

887
00:37:04,974 --> 00:37:06,058
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, whatever
you say, Kevin.</b></i></font>

888
00:37:09,979 --> 00:37:12,064
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know I haven't told you
why I'm in here, Mike.</b></i></font>

889
00:37:16,027 --> 00:37:17,320
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But you don't understand.</b></i></font>

890
00:37:17,778 --> 00:37:20,072
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>From the second I got here,
I've had to watch what I say.</b></i></font>

891
00:37:20,156 --> 00:37:21,824
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Every single word.</b></i></font>

892
00:37:22,992 --> 00:37:25,453
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And every morning,
I get up and I remind myself</b></i></font>

893
00:37:25,536 --> 00:37:28,039
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>not to say the wrong thing
to the wrong person.</b></i></font>

894
00:37:28,164 --> 00:37:30,499
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And every night,
I go to bed and think...</b></i></font>

895
00:37:31,792 --> 00:37:33,294
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Another day down
where I didn't.</b></i></font>

896
00:37:33,377 --> 00:37:35,171
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, you think I don't know
what that's like?</b></i></font>

897
00:37:37,131 --> 00:37:39,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've been living a lie
every day for years.</b></i></font>

898
00:37:39,175 --> 00:37:40,885
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yeah, but you were just
protecting yourself.</b></i></font>

899
00:37:43,179 --> 00:37:44,597
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You don't have a family.</b></i></font>

900
00:37:49,685 --> 00:37:51,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Kevin...</b></i></font>

901
00:37:51,896 --> 00:37:53,147
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What did you do?</b></i></font>

902
00:37:58,861 --> 00:38:00,488
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I got in a fight
with my wife.</b></i></font>

903
00:38:02,531 --> 00:38:03,532
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It was...</b></i></font>

904
00:38:04,909 --> 00:38:05,952
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It was bad.</b></i></font>

905
00:38:07,745 --> 00:38:09,497
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We said things to each other
we never said before.</b></i></font>

906
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,706
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I went out...</b></i></font>

907
00:38:13,459 --> 00:38:14,502
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I got drunk.</b></i></font>

908
00:38:16,087 --> 00:38:17,797
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I got into my car and...</b></i></font>

909
00:38:18,923 --> 00:38:20,341
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I almost killed someone.</b></i></font>

910
00:38:22,051 --> 00:38:23,761
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The next thing I knew,
I woke up in an ambulance</b></i></font>

911
00:38:23,844 --> 00:38:25,388
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>looking up
at a police officer.</b></i></font>

912
00:38:28,224 --> 00:38:29,266
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

913
00:38:29,725 --> 00:38:30,893
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I made one</b></i></font>

914
00:38:32,144 --> 00:38:34,563
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>stupid, stupid mistake.</b></i></font>

915
00:38:37,858 --> 00:38:40,403
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And it's going to cost me
three years with my family.</b></i></font>

916
00:38:41,862 --> 00:38:44,323
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And it's not just
the special things, man.</b></i></font>

917
00:38:44,407 --> 00:38:46,534
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm missing
a thousand chances</b></i></font>

918
00:38:46,617 --> 00:38:48,202
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to hug my kids
in the morning</b></i></font>

919
00:38:49,745 --> 00:38:51,080
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(VOICE BREAKING)
and kiss my wife good night.</b></i></font>

920
00:38:52,915 --> 00:38:55,710
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>All because
I couldn't control myself.</b></i></font>

921
00:38:58,087 --> 00:38:59,922
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What were you fighting
with your wife about?</b></i></font>

922
00:39:01,132 --> 00:39:03,676
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean you were
trying to protect your family?</b></i></font>

923
00:39:04,677 --> 00:39:05,678
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Kevin...</b></i></font>

924
00:39:05,761 --> 00:39:07,596
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>(SNIFFLES) I can't.
Yeah, I can't.</b></i></font>

925
00:39:09,473 --> 00:39:10,766
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just can't.</b></i></font>

926
00:39:31,495 --> 00:39:32,538
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay.</b></i></font>

927
00:39:33,789 --> 00:39:34,874
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'll do it.</b></i></font>

928
00:39:36,751 --> 00:39:38,753
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Excuse me?
Your pro bono.</b></i></font>

929
00:39:38,836 --> 00:39:40,463
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Bring me the file
tomorrow morning.</b></i></font>

930
00:39:42,048 --> 00:39:45,009
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Jessica, I'm sorry.
Can I just ask why?</b></i></font>

931
00:39:45,217 --> 00:39:46,260
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What does it matter?</b></i></font>

932
00:39:47,303 --> 00:39:48,554
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It matters to me.</b></i></font>

933
00:39:49,388 --> 00:39:52,683
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've been out all day
trying to drum up business</b></i></font>

934
00:39:52,767 --> 00:39:54,143
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and it hasn't been easy.</b></i></font>

935
00:39:54,477 --> 00:39:56,896
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, from now on,
when people Google our name,</b></i></font>

936
00:39:56,979 --> 00:39:58,230
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'd rather they see</b></i></font>

937
00:39:59,231 --> 00:40:02,151
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>"Innocent man freed
by Pearson Specter"</b></i></font>

938
00:40:03,694 --> 00:40:05,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>than "Manhattan law firm
hires a fraud."</b></i></font>

939
00:40:07,740 --> 00:40:08,908
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you.</b></i></font>

940
00:40:10,284 --> 00:40:11,535
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Good night, Rachel.</b></i></font>

941
00:40:19,293 --> 00:40:20,586
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
doing here, Sean?</b></i></font>

942
00:40:20,669 --> 00:40:22,546
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, you know what
I'm doing here.</b></i></font>

943
00:40:22,630 --> 00:40:25,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What were you thinking,
trying to get me
thrown off my own case?</b></i></font>

944
00:40:25,174 --> 00:40:26,258
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He was coming at me.</b></i></font>

945
00:40:26,342 --> 00:40:28,010
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I had to do something
to keep his trust.</b></i></font>

946
00:40:28,177 --> 00:40:30,429
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, for your information,
if I get thrown
off this case,</b></i></font>

947
00:40:30,513 --> 00:40:32,139
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that deal that
you don't know about,</b></i></font>

948
00:40:32,223 --> 00:40:33,599
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>getting that certain
someone out early,</b></i></font>

949
00:40:33,682 --> 00:40:34,809
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>doesn't exist anymore.</b></i></font>

950
00:40:34,850 --> 00:40:36,268
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You think
I don't know that?
No.</b></i></font>

951
00:40:36,352 --> 00:40:37,603
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't think you do.</b></i></font>

952
00:40:37,686 --> 00:40:39,105
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because if I hadn't pulled
that shit out of my ass,</b></i></font>

953
00:40:39,188 --> 00:40:40,564
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>this whole thing would
have been for nothing.</b></i></font>

954
00:40:42,233 --> 00:40:43,734
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you so pleased
with yourself about?</b></i></font>

955
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:45,694
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Nothing, it's just...</b></i></font>

956
00:40:45,778 --> 00:40:47,655
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You didn't want me
to take this case.</b></i></font>

957
00:40:47,738 --> 00:40:49,031
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And now,
you're getting pissed at me</b></i></font>

958
00:40:49,115 --> 00:40:51,700
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>because I'm doing too good
a job defending my client.</b></i></font>

959
00:40:53,035 --> 00:40:54,370
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now that you
put it that way...</b></i></font>

960
00:40:55,538 --> 00:40:56,997
